Endung'okinoto e nkiguana e Nkai


1  Atoduaa nanu Olaitoriani eitashe te mbata olperere lo lasar, nejo ninye: “Toosho lukuny oo ng'apeta, o meikirikirata ntonat oo ng'apeta, tebelibelaki ninche inchumat oo ilukuny oo ltung'ana pooki; ore ilooleku lenye naar nanu ninche to lalem; melo ninye obo lenye aisik nemeimisho ninye obo lenye.


2  “Ore hoo naaji ninye te netur enkop aapuo enemeneng'a, naa keitayu ake enkaina ai ninche te ine, ore hoo naaji ninye tenaa keilep aapuo shumata, naa kaitadou nanu ninche te ine. 
3  Ore hoo naaji ninye tenaa keisudori te nchumata oldoinyo oji Karmel naa kaing'oru nanu ninche naitayu ninche; naa ore hoo naaji ninye tenaa keisudori too nkonyek aainei aapuo abori enaiposha naa kairriwaa nanu olasurai ine metoonyo ninche. 
4  Naa ore naaji tenaa kepuo ninche eyararoto te dukuya ilmang'ati lenye, naitanap nanu olalem teine pee ear ninche naa kaing'or nanu ninche te ntorroni neme te sidai.”


5  Ore Olaitoriani, Enkai oo lororani,

ilo laa te neiseyie enkop neshola,

ore lelo pooki oomanya atua neishir to sina

nedumunye pooki anaa olkeju le Nail,

neitoki adou, anaa olkeju le Nail te Misiri;


6  ilo oshet enkaji enye e shumata te keper

nepik olkitamanyunoto lenye shumata enkop

ilo oipotu nkariak e naiposha

nebukoki ninche shumata oriong e nkop

Olaitoriani ninye enkarna enye.


7  “Aimitiuu intae anaa Olosho le Etiopia te nanu, intae lo tung'ana le Israel?” Olaitoriani ojo. “Keitu nanu aitayu ailepunye Israel aitung'uaa enkop e Misiri naitung'uaa Ilfilisti Kafta naitung'uaa Siria Kir? 
8  Ng'ura, etii nkonyek o Laitoriani Enkai shumata enkitoria oo ng'ok, naa kaidaikie nanu aitung'uaa oriong e nkop; Meteleku ake nchere maidaikie nanu tukul enkaji e Yakobo,” Olaitoriani ojo. 
9  “Amu ng'ura, kaitanapisho nanu, pee aipirripir asilu nanu enkaji e Israel tiatua loreren pooki anaa enasil oltung'ani te silet, kake meetae olantererai odoiki enkop. 
10  Ore lelo aing'okok loo ltung'ana laainei pooki naa keye to lalem, lelo oojo, ‘Meinepu ae kata entorroni iyiook aashu etum iyiook.’

Errinyunoto nayookini aarrinyu Israel


11   “Ore akenya te ina olong naitasheiyie nanu enkaji e Daudi apa naturori naitobir nanu ineetarruoitie, nashumu nanu ineeturori, naitoki nanu ashet metotiuo anaa apa. 
12  Pee etum ninche aawaita olpisiai le Edom o lelo oreren pooki ooipoti te nkarna ai,” Olaitoriani ilo oas ena, ojo nji.


13  “Ng'ura, kepuonu nkolong'i,” Olaitoriani ojo,

“ore ilo oturisho neinepu ilo oisampisho

ore ilo oirony ilng'anayio neinepu ilo ounisho;

ore ildoinyo neitong'u enaisho namelok,

neruko too ildoinyo pooki.


14  Kashuku nanu emunyani oo ltung'ana laainei Israel

naa keshet ninche nkanas apa naaidaaitie nemany ninche;

keun ninche isabibu neok enaisho enye;

naa keitayu ninche nkurman neya ilng'anayio lenye.


15  Kaun nanu ninche te nkop enye,

nemeigili ae kata aadotu ninche,

aaitayu tiatua ina kop naishoo nanu ninche,”

Olaitoriani Enkai ojo.

